description: This Chainlink VRF top 2% rating Gatinho purrs with a rating of 88, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 88, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Stringalong for North, Box for East, Stringalong for South, and 1 for West. Gatinho has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/50881-74712-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gatinho [88 Votes, Top 2% Rating]
